<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57"><a href="#calculate-assessed-tax-registers" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Calculate assessed tax registers</a></li>
