<ol sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">Tax &gt; Indirect taxes &gt; Sales tax &gt; Sales tax codes</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="84">Create a sales tax code.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Type of tax</strong> field, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Assessed tax</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="86">Specify the settlement period and the ledger posting group.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">On the Action Pane, on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Sales tax code</strong> tab, in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Sales tax code</strong> group, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Values</strong> to open the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Sales tax code values</strong> page.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">Value</strong> field, specify the tax rate for the assessed tax.</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="set-up-budget-revenue-codes-for-assessed-tax" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">Set up budget revenue codes for assessed tax</h3>
