<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">Cash and bank management &gt; Setup &gt; Payment order setup &gt; Budget revenue classification</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="93">Create a budget revenue code for assessed tax.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="94">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="94">SSGS</strong> check box to indicate that the budget revenue code belongs to the Standard System of Gas Supply (SSGS).</li>
</ol>
