<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="98">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="98">Fixed assets (Russia) &gt; Setup &gt; Tax reporting &gt; Sales tax relations</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="99">Create a record.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="100">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="100">Type of tax</strong> field, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="100">Assessed tax</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="101">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="101">Code</strong> field, select the sales tax code for the assessed tax.</li>
