<ol sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146">Organization administration &gt; Organizations &gt; Legal entities</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="147"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="147">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="147">Addresses</strong> FastTab, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="147">More options &gt; Advanced</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148">Manage addresses</strong> page, on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148">Registration ID</strong> FastTab, create a line.</p>
