<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="149"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="149">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="149">Registration type</strong> field, select the registration type for OKATO/OKTMO.</p>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="151">If the required registration type isn't listed, follow these steps:</p>
