<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="153">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="153">Registration types</strong> page (<strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="153">Organization administration &gt; Global address book &gt; Registration types &gt; Registration types</strong>), create a registration type.</li>
