<h3 id="optional-set-up-company-divisions-their-registration-reason-codes-kpp-and-their-oktmo-codes" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="176">Optional: Set up company divisions, their registration reason codes (KPP), and their OKTMO codes</h3>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="178">If the organization has realty objects that are located in territories that differ from the organization's main location, or if the organization has separate subdivisions, you should set up company divisions.</p>
