<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="180"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="180">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="180">Organization administration &gt; Setup &gt; Separate divisions</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="181"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="181">Create a company division.</p>
