<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="185"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="185">Define the OKTMO code of the company division on the vendor account:</p>
