<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="187">In the vendor account record, on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="187">Addresses</strong> FastTab, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="187">More options &gt; Advanced</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="188">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="188">Registration ID</strong> FastTab, add a line.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="189">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="189">Registration type</strong> field, select the registration type for OKATO/OKTMO.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="190">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="190">Registration number</strong> field, enter the OKTMO code.</li>
