<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="192"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="192">Repeat step 6 to define the KPP code of the separate division on the vendor account. In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="192">Registration type</strong> field, select the registration type that is associated with the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="192">KPP</strong> registration category.</p>
