<h3 id="generate-an-assessed-tax-declaration-1" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="441">Generate an assessed tax declaration</h3>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-assessed-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="443">Before you can generate the assessed tax declaration for a tax year, you must calculate the assessed tax register for the same year, and assessed tax registers for the first, second, and third quarters.</p>
